General.Name: Straker Limited
General.Description: Straker Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the provision of language and subscription services in the Asia Pacific, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and North America. The company operates AI-POWERED RAY, a suite of customizable AI and automation translation tools that creates a first draft translation and matching the customer's content. It also provides RAY language cloud, enterprise, and cloud, as well as slack app and connectors. In addition, the company offers interpreting services. The company was formerly known as Straker Translations Limited and changed its name to Straker Limited in August 2023. Straker Limited was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Auckland, New Zealand.
